% Personal Profile
\section{\faUser\hspace{0.5em} Personal Profile}
\vspace{-0.2cm} 
Aspiring Quality Assurance Engineer with hands-on experience in manual testing, including test case design, execution, defect tracking, and regression testing in real-world projects. Skilled in ensuring product quality and validating complex systems, including AI and security features. Experience on test automation using Playwright, Selenium, and JUnit. Proficient in using GitHub for version control and JIRA for defect tracking. Passionate about contributing to quality-driven teams and committed to continuous learning and delivering
high-quality software.


